[The virus continues its spread in Switzerland. An updated map of its distribution is available at the source URL above. The spread in southward and eastward direction included also the eastern canton of Appenzell, on Austria's border.

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map of Switzerland can be seen at http://healthmap.org/r/1AFv. - Mod.AS]

